14 WHEREAS, Sara Grace has personified the selfless dedication, mental agility, verbal
15 adroitness, and personal maturity necessary for superlative academic performance; and
16 WHEREAS, a proper quality education for the young people of this state is the single most
17 important objective of the General Assembly, and Sara Grace has shown by academic
18 accomplishment that the pursuit and attainment of scholastic success are within the reach of
19 the students in this state; and
20 WHEREAS, the State of Georgia looks with great anticipation toward the future of this
21 bright and promising young citizen.
22 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
23 the members of this body heartily commend Sara Grace Abernathy for being named Model
24 High School's 2025 STAR Student and express their most sincere best wishes for continued
25 academic success.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
27 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Sara
28 Grace Abernathy.
